# Cursor Rules - NINE20 Official Web

## Rule Priority
1. `AGENTS.md` (authoritative)
2. This file
3. Other docs

## Always Do
- Verify with evidence before claiming completion.
- Keep code changes and doc changes in the same task.
- Append a log entry to `MEMORY.md` for each completed task.

## i18n
- Locales: `ko`, `en`, `ja`, `zh-CN`, `zh-TW`, `es`, `fr`
- `zh` should map to `zh-CN`
- No hardcoded user-facing text in components.

## Implementation Conventions
- Next.js 16 async params for `[lang]`
- Keep Tailwind v4 tokens in `src/app/globals.css`
- Prefer small patches and explicit file references

## Required Verification
- `npm test`
- `npm run build` for route/layout/i18n changes

## Task Close Checklist
- Requirement implemented
- Verification passed
- Docs synced (`README.md` if needed)
- `MEMORY.md` updated
